**Title:** Heliocentrism, Part II

**Date:** 1610,  see: https://cudl.lib.cam.ac.uk/view/PR-ADAMS-00005-00061-00001/5

**Intro:** Galilei argues for heliocentrism following his observations through the telescope.

**Category:** Research Tragedies

